title: The Black Arrow - Robert Louis Stevenson  (Unabridged)
description:
The Black Arrow

UNABRIDGED 

Written by Robert Louis Stevenson 

Narrated by Ron Keith


The 15th-century Wars of the Roses serve as backdrop for this swashbuckling historical novel from the author of Kidnapped and Treasure Island.

In a time of shifting loyalties and trecherous alliances, young Dick Shelton is betrayed by his brutal guardian.
